summary: I feel like I’m one of the few people who refuses to reblog pictures and gifsets of the kiss from New Earth. That is NOT ROSE....
body: I feel like I’m one of the few people who refuses to reblog pictures and gifsets of the kiss from New Earth. That is NOT ROSE. That is Cassandra in her body kissing The Doctor without his consent and if he had known it was her at the time he would have been disgusted and furious. I wish people would stop obsessing over and romantasizing that kiss. It’s disgusting and it’s not right. It is not The Doctor and Rose sharing a consensual and wanted kiss, it is a villain tricking him into thinking she’s someone she’s not and snogging him for her own kicks. It’s not right.
